      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Jinshan Xiong\t\t11:49 AM\n\n> Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n> In theory, echo_client can stack upon LOV layer, and then user can pass in a stripe layout to create a striped echo object.\n\nNeither LOV nor our utils support this.\n\n> If we adapt this change we're going to lose this capability. I tend to discuss this before making a decision.\n\nWe lost it some time ago and no one missed it. If you want to add this functionality back then fine but it needs to be in line with LSM encapsulation and should probably happen after LSM encapsulation.",
